A LITTLE BIT
UNSETTLING.

15:18.291 --> 15:20.875
ARE YOU READY?

15:20.875 --> 15:22.750
ARE YOU CURRENTLY
SEXUALLY ACTIVE?

15:24.500 --> 15:25.917
