THAT THERE IS
CURRENTLY NO CURE

15:44.959 --> 15:46.792
FOR THE SEXUALLY
TRANSMITTED DISEASES

15:46.792 --> 15:50.583
HERPES, HIV, AND HPV?

15:50.583 --> 15:52.417
AND ARE YOU AWARE
THAT WHILE THE PILL

15:52.417 --> 15:54.834
OFFERS EXCELLENT PROTECTION
AGAINST PREGNANCY,

15:54.834 --> 15:55.792
