15:55.792 --> 15:58.458
AGAINST SEXUALLY
TRANSMITTED DISEASES?

15:58.458 --> 16:00.625
HAVE YOU HAD
SEXUAL RELATIONS
IN THE PAST,

16:00.625 --> 16:04.583
