WHY YOU'D THINK

16:13.959 --> 16:15.458
YOUR PARTNER'S
NOT BEING MONOGAMOUS?

16:15.458 --> 16:16.750
OH, NO, NO! I--
I WAS JUST KIDDING.

16:16.750 --> 16:17.917
HE'S DEFINITELY
MONOG--

16:17.917 --> 16:19.875
YOU KNOW, JOEY,
SOMETIMES WE THINK
OUR PARTNER

16:19.875 --> 16:20.875
IS BEING MONOGAMOUS--

16:20.875 --> 16:22.125
NO, HE'S DEFINITELY
MONOGAMOUS.

16:22.125 --> 16:25.458
