NO DOUBT IN MY MIND.

16:25.458 --> 16:27.166
REGARDLESS, IT'S IMPORTANT
TO PRACTICE SAFE SEX.

16:27.166 --> 16:30.291
NOW, IS YOUR PARTNER
WILLING TO WEAR CONDOMS?

16:32.959 --> 16:34.166
YES.

16:34.166 --> 16:38.291
MS. POTTER,
THESE AREN'T EVEN
THE HARD QUESTIONS.

16:38.291 --> 16:39.875
WHAT IF YOU
BECOME PREGNANT

16:39.875 --> 16:41.875
OR CONTRACT AN STD?

16:41.875 --> 16:44.625
