THE POTENTIAL
CONSEQUENCES OF SEX.

16:46.208 --> 16:49.125
OK. MAYBE
YOU SHOULD KNOW

16:49.125 --> 16:51.750
THE OTHER SIDE
OF THE COIN, JOEY.

16:51.750 --> 16:55.291
I MEAN, SEX CAN BE
A WONDERFUL, FUN,

16:55.291 --> 16:56.834
FULFILLING
PART OF LIFE.

16:56.834 --> 16:58.667
THERE'S NOTHING
TO BE ASHAMED
OR AFRAID OF.

16:58.667 --> 16:59.917
I JUST...

16:59.917 --> 17:02.834
WANT YOU
TO APPROACH IT

17:02.834 --> 17:05.040
WITH A CERTAIN LEVEL
OF MATURITY

17:05.040 --> 17:06.165
AND RESPONSIBILITY,
THAT'S ALL.

17:07.834 --> 17:10.916
OK. SO YOU SCHEDULED

17:10.916 --> 17:13.666
YOUR PELVIC EXAM
FOR NEXT WEEK.

17:13.666 --> 17:16.208
