HERE YOU GO.

17:16.208 --> 17:19.750
CONDOMS, SPERMICIDE,
SOME INFORMATION
ABOUT BIRTH CONTROL,

17:19.750 --> 17:22.916
DEPO-PROVERA,
OTHER BIRTH CONTROL
OPTIONS.

17:26.375 --> 17:27.916
AND JOEY?

17:27.916 --> 17:29.125
