"SOCCER COACH"
ON MY COLLEGE APPS,

18:28.208 --> 18:30.375
NOT "GAY
CIVIL RIGHTS
CRUSADER."

18:30.375 --> 18:33.542
ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.
I'LL HELP YOU OUT
WITH THIS.

18:33.542 --> 18:34.625
YEAH, THANKS.

18:34.625 --> 18:37.083
OH, AND, UH, JACK?
YOU KNOW, I JUST HOPE

18:37.083 --> 18:39.333
