DAWSON?

19:11.583 --> 19:13.959
IT'S ABOUT
HOW I REACTED

19:13.959 --> 19:15.792
WHEN I FOUND OUT
THAT MOM
WAS PREGNANT.

19:15.792 --> 19:17.959
UM...

19:17.959 --> 19:19.750
I WAS
REALLY SHOCKED

19:19.750 --> 19:22.083
AND, UM...

19:22.083 --> 19:24.250
MAYBE
A LITTLE BIT
DISAPPOINTED,

19:24.250 --> 19:25.375
BUT I'VE BEEN
THINKING,

19:25.375 --> 19:27.583
AND I'VE JUST--
I'VE REALIZED
THAT...

19:27.583 --> 19:31.125
HEH!
THIS IS AMAZING.
I MEAN...

19:32.166 --> 19:33.333
GOD, I'M--
I'M GONNA HAVE

19:33.333 --> 19:34.542
A LITTLE BROTHER
OR SISTER.

19:34.542 --> 19:35.667
I MEAN, HOW COOL
IS THAT?

19:35.667 --> 19:38.083
DAWSON...

19:38.083 --> 19:40.291
WE'RE NOT
GONNA HAVE THE BABY.

19:42.583 --> 19:43.959
WHAT?

19:43.959 --> 19:46.667
I KNOW.

19:46.667 --> 19:49.000
BELIEVE ME,
THIS ISN'T EXACTLY

19:49.000 --> 19:50.583
THE WAY THAT WE
WANTED TO TELL YOU.

19:50.583 --> 19:52.917
YOU KNOW,
W-WAIT A SEC--

19:52.917 --> 19:55.583
J-JUST...

19:55.583 --> 19:57.834
JUST LIKE THAT?

19:57.834 --> 19:59.542
YOU MAKE A DECISION
LIKE THIS IN A DAY?

19:59.542 --> 20:02.291
UH, WELL, NO,
ACTUALLY, DAWSON,

20:02.291 --> 20:03.834
IT WASN'T
JUST LIKE THAT.

20:03.834 --> 20:05.792
I HAD SUSPECTED

20:05.792 --> 20:08.000
THAT I WAS PREGNANT
FOR SOME TIME.

20:08.000 --> 20:09.208
I JUST DIDN'T
WANNA DEAL WITH IT

20:09.208 --> 20:11.583
BECAUSE I KNEW
WHAT MY DECISION
WOULD BE IF I WAS.

20:15.417 --> 20:16.291
I CAN'T
BELIEVE THIS.

20:16.291 --> 20:19.041
WELL, HONEY,
YOU SHOULD BE HAPPY.

20:19.041 --> 20:21.208
YOUR LACKLUSTER ATTEMPT
AT EXCITEMENT JUST NOW

20:21.208 --> 20:22.875
WASN'T EXACTLY
OSCAR-WORTHY.

20:22.875 --> 20:24.375
MOM, I MEANT
EVERYTHING
THAT I SAID.

20:24.375 --> 20:26.000
I'M TRYING TO BE
SUPPORTIVE.

20:31.542 --> 20:32.750
DAD, YOU ACTUALLY
AGREED TO THIS?

20:32.750 --> 20:34.333
YES, I DID.

20:34.333 --> 20:37.583
NO, DAWSON.
HE'S LYING TO PROTECT ME.

20:37.583 --> 20:39.000
IT WAS MY IDEA
AND MY SUGGESTION.

20:39.000 --> 20:42.542
AND YES, I KNOW.

20:42.542 --> 20:44.000
I'M A TERRIBLE MOTHER,
AREN'T I?

20:44.000 --> 20:45.834
TH-THAT'S NOT
WHAT I SAID.

20:45.834 --> 20:48.166
LET'S NOT PRETEND
IT'S NOT WHAT
YOU THINK, HONEY.

20:48.166 --> 20:50.542
IT'S NO LIE
THAT I HAVE MESSED UP

20:50.542 --> 20:52.417
AT BEING YOUR MOTHER
AT EVERY TURN,

20:52.417 --> 20:54.417
THAT I'M THE ONE
THAT TORE
YOUR FAMILY APART--

20:54.417 --> 20:57.166
WAIT A--
D-DON'T USE ME
AS THE EXCUSE

20:57.166 --> 20:59.417
FOR MAKING
THIS DECISION.
THAT'S NOT FAIR.

20:59.417 --> 21:01.667
IT'S NOT AN EXCUSE,
DAWSON.

21:01.667 --> 21:05.625
NO, I SAT DOWN,
AND I CONSIDERED
ALL THE FACTS.

21:05.625 --> 21:08.750
AND THE FACT IS...

21:08.750 --> 21:11.083
I CAN'T DO IT AGAIN.

21:11.083 --> 21:13.834
I CAN'T HANDLE
THE MISTAKES.

21:13.834 --> 21:16.125
NOW, YOU PUT
THAT TOGETHER
WITH THE MONEY ISSUES

21:16.125 --> 21:18.667
AND MY AGE
AND EVERYTHING ELSE,

21:18.667 --> 21:20.583
AND THE ONLY ANSWER
IS...

21:21.208 --> 21:25.625
I CAN'T HAVE THE BABY.

21:25.625 --> 21:26.917
NOW, HONEY, MAYBE YOU'RE
GONNA HATE ME FOREVER

21:26.917 --> 21:29.250
BECAUSE OF THIS,

21:29.250 --> 21:31.166
OR MAYBE YOU'LL
NEVER BE ABLE
TO UNDERSTAND,

21:31.166 --> 21:34.041
BUT THE FACT IS...

21:34.041 --> 21:36.125
THIS IS MY DECISION,

21:36.125 --> 21:38.291
AND I HAVE MADE IT.

21:38.291 --> 21:43.250
AND NOW
THIS DISCUSSION...

21:43.250 --> 21:44.625
IT'S OVER.

22:00.125 --> 22:04.125
