TO TELL YOU

22:19.375 --> 22:22.458
THAT BREAKFAST
IS READY.

22:22.458 --> 22:25.250
WELL, TELL MY MOTHER
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

22:28.000 --> 22:29.250
SHE ALSO WANTED ME
TO TELL YOU

22:29.250 --> 22:32.166
THAT SHE'S SORRY
YOU'RE UPSET.

22:32.166 --> 22:33.625
AND I CAN
PERSONALLY ATTEST

22:33.625 --> 22:36.458
TO HER NOT SLEEPING
A WINK LAST NIGHT.

22:39.166 --> 22:40.667
IS SHE REALLY
GONNA DO THIS?

22:40.667 --> 22:41.792
YES.

22:44.750 --> 22:46.041
WHAT ABOUT YOU?

22:46.041 --> 22:48.417
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

22:48.417 --> 22:50.583
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I WANT.

22:52.542 --> 22:55.166
BUT I DO KNOW
THAT I DON'T
WANT HER

22:55.166 --> 22:56.291
GOING THROUGH
WITH THE PREGNANCY

22:56.291 --> 23:00.375
IF IT'S NOT
THE RIGHT THING
FOR HER TO DO.

23:00.375 --> 23:03.542
ULTIMATELY
IT'S HER BODY,
HER DECISION.

23:03.542 --> 23:04.708
I RESPECT THAT.

23:08.458 --> 23:11.125
WHAT IF IT'S
THE WRONG DECISION?

23:18.708 --> 23:19.959
DID I EVER TELL YOU

23:19.959 --> 23:21.667
THAT WE TRIED
FOR 3 YEARS
TO GET PREGNANT

23:21.667 --> 23:22.000
BEFORE WE HAD YOU?

23:22.000 --> 23:23.917
NO.

23:23.917 --> 23:26.708
YEAH.
WE'D JUST ABOUT GIVEN UP.

23:26.708 --> 23:31.417
AND THEN,
AFTER YOU WERE BORN,
WE TRIED AGAIN.

23:32.542 --> 23:35.583
5 YEARS OF HOPE
AND DISAPPOINTMENT.

23:35.583 --> 23:39.542
I HAD ALWAYS WANTED
A BIG FAMILY, YOU KNOW.

23:39.542 --> 23:43.542
A HOUSE FILLED
WITH LOVE
AND ALL THAT.

23:43.542 --> 23:45.667
ADMITTING
THAT IT WOULD
NEVER HAPPEN...

23:48.083 --> 23:50.750
THAT WAS DEVASTATING.

23:50.750 --> 23:53.500
BUT THEN, ONE MORNING,
I WOKE UP...

23:53.500 --> 23:57.291
I REALIZED
THAT IT DID HAPPEN.

23:57.291 --> 24:00.917
MY HOUSE
IS FILLED WITH LOVE,
AND MY LIFE IS FULL.

24:02.417 --> 24:04.291
I DON'T KNOW.
MAYBE FOR THE REST
OF MY LIFE,

24:04.291 --> 24:06.250
I'LL WONDER, "WHAT IF?"

24:06.250 --> 24:09.500
BUT NOW...

24:09.500 --> 24:12.250
I AM JUST SO GRATEFUL
TO HAVE YOU.

24:14.000 --> 24:16.250
AND YOUR MOTHER.

24:16.250 --> 24:18.583
MAKES ALL THE REST
EASIER TO DEAL WITH.

24:41.083 --> 24:44.458
Bessie: JOEY,
WOULD YOU PLEASE TELL
YOUR STUPID BOYFRIEND

24:44.458 --> 24:47.166
